title: Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban (2004) [1080p]
description:
Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban (2004) 7.8/10
Something wicked this way comes. - Harry, Ron and Hermione return to Hogwarts for another magic-filled year. Harry comes face to face with danger yet again, this time in the form of escaped convict, Sirius Black – and turns to sympathetic Professor Lupin for help.

Director: Alfonso Cuarón
Rating: 7.8 / 10
Genre: Adventure, Fantasy, Family
Starring: Daniel Radcliffe, Emma Watson, Rupert Grint
